en_822839_0	58 Division troops organized a full-day adventure training workshop for differently able woman residents in the Equality-based Community Support and Training Centre (ECSAT) in Galle on 28 December 2018 at the 58 Division Headquarters premises in Boossa.
en_822839_1	The programme was organized on the directions of the General Officer Commanding 58 Division, Major General Sudath Perera responding to a request made by ECSAT authorities for assistance.
en_822839_2	20 differently able women participated in the workshop and received training to face challenges and improve confidence.
en_822839_3	58 Division Deputy GOC, Senior Officers and members of the ECSAT attended the workshop.
